261
00:11:13,910 --> 00:11:15,530
You looked really cool!

262
00:11:15,990 --> 00:11:18,870
Hachimitsu, you were seriously amazing!

263
00:11:18,870 --> 00:11:21,180
You really are a riot, Hachimitsu!

264
00:11:21,630 --> 00:11:22,940
